title: DG ISPR felicitates team Pakistan on qualifying for T20 World Cup’s final
content:
RAWALPINDI, Nov 09 (APP): The Director General Inter-Services Public Relations (DG ISPR) on Wednesday extended felicitations to National Cricket Team on qualifying for T20 World Cup’s finals .
In a tweet on his official twitter handle, Major General Babar Iftikhar wrote, “Congratulations Team Pakistan for a stellar performance and winning #SemiFinalT20WC.”
He further said, “Good luck for the Final. Pakistan Zindabad!”
